We’re thrilled to be part of @fwecanada Money Moves program supporting women entrepreneurs with the right tools to help fund their businesses.
.
Our co-founder @ravymehroke will be speaking to the group this Thursday of her own experience funding Bombay Brow Bar, along with Kara Sam from @buchabrew. These fierce ladies will be of 28 inspiring speakers throughout the four week online course, live to 6 different provinces.
.
Are you a woman entrepreneur looking for funding for your business? This course is now full but the next one begins Spring 2011. Don’t miss your seat again. Sign up to be part of the wait list by visiting @fwecanada to register.
.
Let’s raise capital and move forward with our dreams into 2021 💰.
